### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### List all jobs (3 seed jobs load automatically)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/jobs

### Only pending jobs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/jobs?status=pending

### Create a new job
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Leaking faucet in bathroom",
  "customer_name": "John Smith",
  "address": "500 Howard St, Omaha NE 68102",
  "trade_type": "plumbing",
  "assigned_to": "Mike Jimenez"
}

### Update status — paste a real ID from the list response
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/jobs/PASTE-ID-HERE/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "notes": "Tech on site"
}

### Close a job — paste a real ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/jobs/PASTE-ID-HERE/close
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Issue resolved, customer signed off"
}